dict.string: Terminal setups for most frequent projects

on alfred_script(q) tell application "iTerm2" create window with default profile
--- Tab 1 Backend tell first session of current tab of current window set name to "(glossary-tool) Backend" write text "glossary-tool" end tell
tell current window create tab with default profile end tell
--- Tab 2 Frontend tell first session of second tab of current window set name to "(glossary-tool) Frontend" write text "glossary-tool-folder" write text "npm run dev" end tell
tell current window create tab with default profile end tell
--- Tab 3 Git tell first session of third tab of current window set name to "(glossary-tool) Git" write text "glossary-tool-folder" write text "gs" end tell end tell
end alfred_script
